{"tid":1756560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團體促聯國轟警暴","createTime":"2019-11-26T05:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T06:56:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"302265f95dd87bd8b4c28d64f85ce28f73570f3f","tid":1756560,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/PH3DBMYTGKFGN3ALERK7EJEKBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FPH3DBMYTGKFGN3ALERK7EJEKBM%2F&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0y8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=4295b382\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FPH3DBMYTGKFGN3ALERK7EJEKBM%2F&h=3a5a1ad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/PH3DBMYTGKFGN3ALERK7EJEKBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n團體促聯國轟警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191126/large/1574700043_ea8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574700043_ea8f.jpg&h=0cf34c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22個人權組織昨向聯合國人權高級專員米歇爾‧巴切萊特發公開信表達不滿。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處日前針對香港局勢發表聲明，發言人科爾維爾（Rupert Colville）稱「（香港）當局很大程度上尊重和平集會的權利」。國際特赦組織等22個人權組織昨向聯合國人權高級專員米歇爾‧巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）發公開信表達不滿，認為相關聲明否認了由多個可靠來源紀錄的侵犯人權事件，要求對方明確譴責警暴，並譴責特區政府有系統地侵犯和平集會及言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n有份發公開信的人權組織包括國際特赦組織、台灣人權促進會、中國人權捍衞者、世界反酷刑組織及國際人權服務社等，聯署組織批評香港警方系統性地壓制和平集會權，對行使其人權的人使用過度武力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者周 婷"},{"pid":"c524a3d812886e2669ce12807eb66b3151088838","tid":1756560,"uid":143348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b9d2aff14fd290ee33206ed8b42826cb58103e4","tid":1756560,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9313215d829363c67cd5e8532ed8bc152078fb9","tid":1756560,"uid":241069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc72343f873987db820aee7ee2e4e2ddb83de1a","tid":1756560,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"果然有善心人都靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a745557a3b16826b3c7af373abb6a03b675e4cd5","tid":1756560,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地有冇上去攞料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(突發) 有手足收集好多子彈!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0248e1d848eb6f71bf3dfd54c27ab6ae507b9f3c","tid":1756560,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17bf70e45ff4e89808e7097ec478d3d7a95962f","tid":1756560,"uid":88287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97aff4efe48abca6dfb9ba08602be4c688f75c47","tid":1756560,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔係區選贏拎左民意啲團體都唔會走出黎嘈<br />\n即係你地你俾唔到人地睇你地有贏面係唔會有人企出黎幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}